headline: UPS boosts intra-Asia air capacity as US volumes wane
summary: UPS is readjusting its air freight network in response to high demand within Asia as volumes from China to the U.S. decrease. The post UPS boosts intra-Asia air capacity as US volumes wane appeared first on FreightWaves.
